    <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d189.45277274423896!2d49.70816720304945!3d40.558280635520255!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4030911b01f18a9f%3A0x51e4aac4a1be7d44!2sPetrol%20Station!5e0!3m2!1sru!2s!4v1640288120148!5m2!1sru!2s" class="google-map__one" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>

</section>
